	* SourceViewWidget (mouseEvent): Changed variable display to be triggered
	by a menu, added breakpoint status to right click in margin. (bug 
	#1685, bug #1686).

	* SourceBuffer.java (createTags): Refactored to use new DOMTagTypes
	class.
	(addFunction): Ditto.
	(addVariable): Ditto.
	(addKeyword): Ditto.
	(addClass): Ditto.

